SUMMARY:OMSI (Oregon Museum of Science and Industry): First Sunday
DESCRIPTION:Category: Arts & Culture\nCost: $20 adults\; $17 seniors (63+)\
 ; $15 youth (3-13)\; free under 3\; $5 First Sunday\; $5 Arts for All (EBT
 /SNAP/WIC/TANF/Medicaid/OHP)\nNote: Arts for All provides up to 4 tickets 
 at $5 each for EBT/SNAP/WIC/TANF/Medicaid/OHP recipients (any state)\; up 
 to 55% off memberships\nInfo: Discounted admission day - only $5 per perso
 n for all exhibits. Planetarium shows\, submarine tours\, and special exhi
 bitions also $5 each. Purchase tickets online in advance to skip the line.
  Interactive science museum great for families and curious minds.\nAddress
 : 1945 SE Water Ave\, Portland\, OR 97214\nPhone: 503-797-4000\nWebsite: h
 ttps://omsi.edu/
