DESCRIPTION:Category: Arts & Culture\nCost: $10 suggested donation per tour
  (FREE self-guided options available)\nNote: Reservations or donations not
  required but appreciated. Self-guided smartphone tours and PDF downloads 
 are free.\nFormat: In-person\nInfo: Learn about Portland's founders and re
 gionally-known pioneers. Meet at Soldiers Monument.\nAddress: Lone Fir Cem
 etery\, SE 26th Ave & SE Stark St\, Portland\, OR 97214\nWebsite: https://
 www.friendsoflonefircemetery.org\nDetails: 501(c)(3) nonprofit preserving 
 cemetery history since 2000. One of Portland's most beautiful and historic
  green spaces. Final resting place of many Portland pioneers.
