 are free.\nFormat: In-person\nInfo: Highlights notable women including Ter
 williger\, McLoughlin\, Macleay families. Meet at Soldiers Monument.\nAddr
 ess: Lone Fir Cemetery\, SE 26th Ave & SE Stark St\, Portland\, OR 97214\n
